[32m│[0m ("ssti_demo") and Django template configuration, but I cannot confirm it or  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m extract the flag due to the ALLOWED_HOSTS configuration blocking all test    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m requests. The technical setup indicates this is a vulnerable application     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m designed for SSTI testing, but the Host header restriction prevents          [32m│[0m
